Absender: D^r^ Heinrich Schenker
III, Reisnerstr. 38.

{verso}
Sonntag 10 ½^h^. Vm.
Liebe Frau Wally,  Writing of this postcard is recorded in Schenker's diary at OJ 2/10, p. 825:  "An Frau Wally (K.): können leider nicht kommen wegen eines Ofen-Zwischenfalles, meiner Erkältung usw."  ("To Wally (postcard): unfortunately we cannot come on account of an incident over the oven, my cold, etc.  ").  The communication from Valerie Violin to Schenker is not known to survive.

